sentences.en: There is a five-year sunset on the new tax.
sentences.cn: 新税种的有效施行期限为五年。

sentences.en: The calls for reform come as intense debate continues among the leadership over the next five-year economic plan.
sentences.cn: 当围绕下一个五年经济计划的激烈争论在领导层中继续时，改革的呼声到来了。

sentences.en: Their five-year relationship was strained beyond breaking point.
sentences.cn: 他们长达5年的关系紧张得超过了极限。
